Acceptance Criteria
	‚Ä¢	Only one request can be selected at a time
	‚Ä¢	Selected request details are displayed
	‚Ä¢	The selected request is used as reference for allocation

‚∏ª

US5 ‚Äî Display stock availability for requested equipment

