Acceptance Criteria
	‚Ä¢	The technician can scan or manually enter an identifier
	‚Ä¢	Search is triggered only by Enter or Search
	‚Ä¢	Automatic search on each character is disabled

‚∏ª

US7 ‚Äî Validate equipment eligibility for allocation

